        <h2 class="section-title">Thoughtful communication is at the heart of <em>effective leadership.</em></h2>
        <p class="about-text">With over two decades of experience in strategic communications, leadership, and team development — particularly within retail and fast-paced environments — I understand the realities leaders face every day.</p>
        <p class="about-text">Before founding Klarity International, I spent nearly seven years as Global Head of Marketing &amp; Communications at Taco Bell International (Yum! Brands), taking a powerhouse domestic brand global across a dozen countries. Most recently, I served as Head of Professional Development &amp; Executive Coach at UCI's Paul Merage School of Business, coaching EMBA students from engineers, program managers to C-level leaders.</p>
        <p class="about-text">My work is grounded, practical, and focused on real-world application. I partner with leaders to help them think more clearly, communicate more effectively, and lead in a way that brings others with them.</p>
